high_descs: Turn left and head to the stove on the other end of the island.
Pick up the knife on the counter to the right of the stove.
Turn right and head to the sink.
Slice the tomato in the sink.
Set the knife down on the counter between the sink and the other knife.
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Turn around and head back to the stove.
Put the tomato slice on the plate to the left of the stove.
Pick up the plate from the counter.
Move a few steps to the microwave on your left.
Put the plate with tomato into the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with tomato slice into the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter to the right of the oven
Grab the knife off of the counter
Turn right and go to the sink
Cut the tomato in the sink into slices
Put the knife down on the counter to the left of the sink
Grab one of the tomato slices out of the sink
Turn around and face the counter to the right of the sink
Put the tomato on the plate on the counter
Grab the plate off of the counter
Turn left and head to the microwave
Put the plate in the microwave
anns.task_desc: Putting a plate with a tomato slice on it in the microwave

high_descs: Turn left to move to the fridge, then head left again to stop at the counter to the right of the stove.
Pick up the butter knife behind the plate on the counter.
Turn right to face the sink.
Use the knife to slice the tomato.
Place the knife on the counter to the left of the sink.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the sink.
Turn left and carry the slice of tomato to stand in front of the plate on the counter to the right of the stove.
Place the tomato slice on the plate.
Pick up the plate with the tomato slice on it from the counter.
Take a step the left to stand in front of the stove and look up to find the microwave above the stove.
Place the plate with the tomato slice on it in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a slice of tomato on a plate in the microwave.
